{
  "stem": "4963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- the Russians, I believe, came in about June 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it might have been a few months earlier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember that right away, it was an upheaval in-- in-- in our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shortly, within a month, people were evicted from their homes, from their stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was nationalized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They brought in-- the Russians just drove my parents out of the store and brought in their own people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it became a government store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just-- they just nationalized the stores, all the wealth from the different people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were permitted to live in one of our houses, mainly because my father knew the so-called lay of the land, all the-- the upkeep, where the different heaters were, the water heaters, and various things.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they permitted him to stay as a janitor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I can even remember in the winter time him having to go out and-- and shovel the snow, and-- and sweep the ground.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were-- and then pretty soon, everything, they used to come into the home and just usurp various goods of-- of-- of value.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I remember my mother putting-- we had a large grand piano, black piano, and she placed it with some Polish people, Polish descent, who lived nearby.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every day I would go-- well, maybe three, four times a week-- I would go and play the piano, practice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so that piano really played a significant part in my life because it saved my life, I think.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, oh, various things I remember that they buried money and converted a lot of the valuables into gold coins and put them in bottles and buried them under the ground-- underground under our house.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
